2005-2-17  Matthias Troyer <troyer@comp-phys.org>

	* [lattice] Added support for determining equivalent distances on
          periodic lattices, as well as momenta and how translations on the
          lattice map to graphs. The latter is in support of Bloch-states in
          the diagonalization codes.

2005-2-08  Matthias Troyer <troyer@comp-phys.org>

	* [expression] Added functions of an arbitrary number of arguments.
          Added atan2 and random number generation functions.
	* [model] Added separate classes and XML descriptions for
          site operators, bond operators, and sums of these operators
          Require the use of site indices also for site operators
	* [model,random] added a global random number generator for the
          expression library for implementing the RNG in expressions
	* [alea] Added labels to vector observables to be used instead of a 
          numerical index

